longBusinessSummary: Tribox Group AB (publ) operates as an environmental technology company in Sweden. It engages in the development and sale of biofuel. The company also offers consumer and professional fuel formulas, two-stroke formula concentrates, and two-stroke injection formulas. Tribox Group AB (publ) was formerly known as Triboron International AB (publ) and changed its name to Tribox Group AB (publ) in June 2025. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Spånga, Sweden.
